# Varieties of Indoctrination (V-Indoc) Dataset

## Overview

The Varieties of Indoctrination (V-Indoc) dataset is a global dataset on the politicization of education and the media. It is created using the V-Dem infrastructure and draws on information provided by 760 country experts. The dataset presents novel indices and indicators on indoctrination efforts in education and the media around the world.

